data.expected_result: The buttons work because the notif neither covers them nor has anything to do with them.
data.short_description: You cannot interact with any button above the in app notification that comes when you aren't able to connect.
data.steps_to_repro: -  Get the in app notif that has the links to the server status page and Discord's Twitter handle (you headache on how you get the notif). - Click on any button above it (i.e. search, open member list button, open channel button).
